rael-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/israeli-justice-minister-most-of-what-i-know-about-the-war-is-from-al-jazeera/0000018f-5797-d6a5-a5ff-d7b709760000</guid></item><item><title>加州大学伯克利分校法学教授因与反以色列学生对抗而展开调查</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/uc-berkeley-opens-probe-into-law-professor-over-confrontation-with-anti-israel-student/0000018f-57bd-d348-a7bf-f7bdcb0e0000</link><description>该学生向大学防止骚扰和歧视办公室提出投诉后展开调查。这位法学教授说：“令人不安的是，那个故意扰乱我家晚宴的学生......然后竟然厚颜无耻地提出投诉。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 11:13:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/uc-berkeley-opens-probe-into-law-professor-over-confrontation-with-anti-israel-student/0000018f-57bd-d348-a7bf-f7bdcb0e0000</guid></item><item><title>布林肯将错过报告以色列是否在加沙违反国际法的最后期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-to-miss-deadline-on-reporting-whether-israel-violating-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-5760-d348-a7bf-f7e9eaa80000</link><description>一位美国官员预计延迟不会持续超过几天。然而，另一位人士指出，周五之后的任何拖延都将不可避免地被视为拜登政府“做假账”</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:22:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/blinken-to-miss-deadline-on-reporting-whether-israel-violating-international-law-in-gaza/0000018f-5760-d348-a7bf-f7e9eaa80000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和他的帮派更喜欢死去的人质，而不是快乐的左翼分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-gang-prefer-dead-hostages-to-happy-leftists/0000018f-539f-d662-a7af-7bbf95030000</link><description>战争已经过去七个月了，将这个以色列邪教成员团结在一起的唯一粘合剂仍然是对任何他们认为是“左派”的事物的深不可测的仇恨</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 10:16:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-08/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-gang-prefer-dead-hostages-to-happy-leftists/0000018f-539f-d662-a7af-7bbf95030000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡上周推动拉法攻势，以色列战时内阁反对</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-pushed-for-rafah-offensive-last-week-israels-war-cabinet-opposed/0000018f-5729-d7a9-adcf-ff3d66880000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡总理的一些行为暗示了推迟达成协议的不可告人的动机。他的办公室否认了此类指控，但尽管以色列官员评估哈马斯即将同意该提议，但内塔尼亚胡不顾战时内阁的反对，开始准备在拉法采取军事行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:26:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-pushed-for-rafah-offensive-last-week-israels-war-cabinet-opposed/0000018f-5729-d7a9-adcf-ff3d66880000</guid></item><item><title>对于流离失所的加沙人来说，离开拉法就是从一个地狱走向另一个地狱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-gazans-leaving-rafah-is-moving-from-one-hell-to-another/0000018f-5411-d348-a7bf-f6b95e5a0000</link><description>以色列军队最近发动了加沙居民的撤离，他们被迫在汗尤尼斯废墟和没有供水和污水基础设施的沿海地带之间做出选择</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:09:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-05-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-displaced-gazans-leaving-rafah-is-moving-from-one-hell-to-another/0000018f-5411-d348-a7bf-f6b95e5a0000</guid></item><item><title>官员称，美国暂停向以色列运送炸弹，以表达对拉法入侵的担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/u-s-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel-to-signal-concerns-over-rafah-invasion-official-says/0000018f-570b-d209-a79f-572be3fa0000</link><description>该官员表示，暂停发货的决定是上周做出的，目前尚未就是否稍后继续发货做出最终决定。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 09:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/u-s-paused-bomb-shipment-to-israel-to-signal-concerns-over-rafah-invasion-official-says/0000018f-570b-d209-a79f-572be3fa0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的联盟看起来很安全，因为就连他的对手也拒绝了哈马斯的停火提议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-looks-safe-as-even-his-opponents-reject-hamas-cease-fire-offer/0000018f-54e7-d209-a79f-54ef7bc10000</link><description>民族团结部长和以色列谈判团队反对加沙恐怖组织的提议，该提议与以色列接受的提议在三个关键方面有所不同，其中包括哈马斯拒绝保证在协议第一阶段释放人质。</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 03:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-coalition-looks-safe-as-even-his-opponents-reject-hamas-cease-fire-offer/0000018f-54e7-d209-a79f-54ef7bc10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列重新开放进入加沙的主要过境点；美国因拉法事件暂停向以色列运送武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-live/u-s-israel-agrees-to-open-kerem-shalom-crossing-for-aid-into-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018f-5600-d0ec-a9cf-de1fb30d0000</link><description>以色列重新开放凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点，为加沙提供援助 ■ 疑似以色列人质于 10 月 7 日被杀，尸体在加沙扣留 ■ 以色列承诺限制拉法行动，将与埃及过境点的控制权授予美国私人公司 ■ 哈马斯代表团在开罗进行人质谈判 ■ 国防加兰特部长：在消灭哈马斯或释放第一名人质之前，拉法行动不会停止</description><pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 02:27:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article-live/u-s-israel-agrees-to-open-kerem-shalom-crossing-for-aid-into-gaza-on-wednesday/0000018f-5600-d0ec-a9cf-de1fb30d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的拉法袭击和停火谈判并不像看上去的那样</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/nothing-about-israels-rafah-attack-and-the-cease-fire-talks-is-quite-what-it-seems/0000018f-5484-d6a5-a5ff-d6a402c80000</link><description>停火迫在眉睫吗？以色列如何才能在谈判达成协议的同时占领拉法口岸？哈马斯和埃及的游戏计划是什么？内塔尼亚胡能否在不跨越拜登红线的情况下安抚本格维尔？以下是如何了解加沙正在发生的事情以及战争是否会很快结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 21:12:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-08/ty-article/.premium/nothing-about-israels-rafah-attack-and-the-cease-fire-talks-is-quite-what-it-seems/0000018f-5484-d6a5-a5ff-d6a402c80000</guid></item><item><title>白宫称以色列和哈马斯之间在停火协议上的分歧可以弥合</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-gaps-between-israel-and-hamas-on-cease-fire-deal-can-be-bridged/0000018f-5491-d209-a79f-54b93a7b0000</link><description>白宫发言人否认美国在哈马斯同意的拟议协议上背着以色列 ■ 拜登政府警告内塔尼亚胡不要扩大拉法的入侵，但也表示对费城路线沿线的行动没有问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 20:53:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/white-house-says-gaps-between-israel-and-hamas-on-cease-fire-deal-can-be-bridged/0000018f-5491-d209-a79f-54b93a7b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列和哈马斯代表团抵达开罗，信号混乱</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-back-in-cairo-amid-mixed-signals/0000018f-5483-d4c7-a3af-fcfb4e360000</link><description>以色列一直在传播相互矛盾的信息。一方面，战时内阁同意继续谈判，另一方面，政治消息人士称谈判是“欺骗”，旨在削弱拉法行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 20:00:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-delegation-back-in-cairo-amid-mixed-signals/0000018f-5483-d4c7-a3af-fcfb4e360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人嘲笑亲巴勒斯坦校园抗议活动是在玩火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-07/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-who-ridicule-pro-palestinian-campus-protests-are-playing-with-fire/0000018f-5399-d4c7-a3af-fffb83820000</link><description>以色列人若不理会这些抗议活动，后果自负。他们的未来在很多方面取决于这些在世界最负盛名的大学草坪上露营的学生所形成的观点，以及他们将对其国家未来政策产生的影响</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 19:56:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-07/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-who-ridicule-pro-palestinian-campus-protests-are-playing-with-fire/0000018f-5399-d4c7-a3af-fffb83820000</guid></item><item><title>人质家庭论坛：疑似人质利奥尔·鲁达夫 (Lior Rudaeff) 于 10 月 7 日被杀，他的尸体被扣押在加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/presumed-hostage-lior-rudaeff-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-is-held-in-gaza/0000018f-5486-d209-a79f-54afd6b50000</link><description>鲁达夫是紧急安全小组的成员，10 月 7 日，他与数十名渗入尼尔伊扎克基布兹的恐怖分子进行了战斗。鲁达夫身后留下了妻子、四个孩子和三个孙子</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 19:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/presumed-hostage-lior-rudaeff-was-killed-on-oct-7-his-body-is-held-in-gaza/0000018f-5486-d209-a79f-54afd6b50000</guid></item><item><title>人质、停火谈判将决定拉法行动的未来</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/hostage-cease-fire-talks-will-determine-the-future-of-rafah-operation/0000018f-544c-d209-a79f-546d94040000</link><description>以色列军队已经控制了拉​​法过境点和费城走廊东部，向哈马斯施压，要求达成人质交易。但这可能会导致对拉法的征服——这有可能导致谈判破裂并危及人质的生命</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 19:17:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/hostage-cease-fire-talks-will-determine-the-future-of-rafah-operation/0000018f-544c-d209-a79f-546d94040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列如何仍能赢得对哈马斯和伊朗的最终胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-israel-can-still-win-the-ultimate-victory-over-hamas-and-iran/0000018f-4ee0-d6c3-afdf-4ff322520000</link><description>以色列的“单干”战略猛然醒悟：它需要美国和阿拉伯盟友更多的支持来对抗伊朗及其恶毒伙伴，包括哈马斯和真主党。拜登的战后计划提供了这条生命线，但总统还应该添加一个元素</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 18:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/how-israel-can-still-win-the-ultimate-victory-over-hamas-and-iran/0000018f-4ee0-d6c3-afdf-4ff322520000</guid></item><item><title>美国缓慢向以色列出售武器引发政策转变问题</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-slow-rolling-weapons-sale-to-israel-sparking-questions-of-policy-shift/0000018f-541a-d6a5-a5ff-d63a538f0000</link><description>尽管拜登政府实际上已暂停向以色列出售武器，但官员们否认了这标志着政策新转变的说法，尽管美以因迫在眉睫的拉法行动而关系紧张</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:58:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-slow-rolling-weapons-sale-to-israel-sparking-questions-of-policy-shift/0000018f-541a-d6a5-a5ff-d63a538f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列发起拉法行动的威胁奏效了——但主要是针对埃及和美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-threat-of-a-rafah-operation-worked-but-mainly-against-egypt-and-the-u-s/0000018f-53ca-d348-a7bf-f7eb45ce0000</link><description>哈马斯的声明开启了达成停火协议的可能性。如果实现的话，也可能影响北部战线，并为与黎巴嫩外交解决打开渠道</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 17:39:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-threat-of-a-rafah-operation-worked-but-mainly-against-egypt-and-the-u-s/0000018f-53ca-d348-a7bf-f7eb45ce0000</guid></item></channel></rss>